ons":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"fresh"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"moist"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"tender, soft, mild"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be fresh, to be still moist, to be yet soft"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ط ر و (ṭ r w) or ط ر ي (ṭ r y); compare طَرُوَ (ṭaruwa, “to be or become fresh, moist, tender”) and طَرِيَ (ṭariya, “(same)”). Cognate with Hebrew טָרִי (ṭārī, “fresh, moist, new”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26484","headword_ar":"طُرَّى","root":"Tr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A she-ass"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"driven away:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) or a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brisk, lively,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"ass. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n26702","headword_ar":"طَرِىٌّ","root":"Trw","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fresh, juicy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moist:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariYo'N","text_ar":"طَرِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var. thereof. (Msb.) It is expl. as meaning thus in the Kur [xvi. 44 and] xxxv. 13 [as an epithet applied to the flesh of fish]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ariy~aAni","text_ar":"الطَّرِيَّانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[used as a subst.] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fish and fresh ripe dates."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stranger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariybN","text_ar":"غَرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and AA has mentioned ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN TaAriY~N","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ طَارِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [said to be] with teshdeed, [otherwise I should think it might be a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAriy^N","text_ar":"طَارِيٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man that is a stranger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}